An app for all sewing fans.
With this app, you can quickly calculate the right amount of material for any garment, find the nearest fabric store, as well as useful and interesting information about fabrics.

The app features four main sections: Calculation, Measurements, Directory, Stores.

Program features:
-	You can calculate the amount of fabric needed for different kinds of clothes: dresses, blouses, skirts, trousers, jackets;
-	The program can produce pattern layout that best fits your calculation parameters;
-	The program offers useful cutout and layout tips for each specific case;
-	You can send calculation results and layouts by e-mail;

-	You can create a list of people with their individual measurements;
-	The app can automatically substitute the measurements of a particular person when calculating the fabric amount for a particular garment;

-	The app can automatically search for the nearest fabrics and accessories stores;
-	When searching for nearest stores, you can choose a search radius: from 500m to 4500m;

-	The program offers five thematic encyclopedias: Prints, Fabric types, Fabric properties, Fabric composition, Interweaving.

There are plans to develop the app further by adding calculations for other garments categories and new useful articles. We would welcome any comments, opinions, suggestions or anything else that would help us improve our app and serve you better.

